Package com.planner.scripter

Class Type

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.planner.scripter.Type
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<Type>
    public class Type
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Type>
    Manages and stores data for the specified variable within the Simple scripting language. It handles all core methods and attributes with regards to the object being handled. Variables within Simple are dynamic in nature and allow storing an instance of any kind. Garbage collection is processed by the JVM.
    Author:
    Andrew Roe
